{
    "ai-tha-ap487:0.1_0": "Therāpadāna",
    "ai-tha-ap487:0.2_0": "Paṁsukūlavagga",
    "ai-tha-ap487:0.3_0": "5. Candanamāliyattheraapadāna",
    "ai-tha-ap487:1.1_0": "“One who’s given up the five sensual titillations,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:1.2_0": "so pleasing and delightful,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:1.3_0": "Uncockshuned goad,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:1.4_0": "and then I went forth to homelessness.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:2.1_0": "After going forth in body,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:2.2_0": "I shunned deeds with evil deeds.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:2.3_0": "Giving up bad verbal conduct,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:2.4_0": "Nadīkassapa.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:3.1_0": "While living here alone",
    "ai-tha-ap487:3.2_0": "the best of Buddhas,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:3.3_0": "I don’t know,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:3.4_0": "that I had done what had happened.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:4.1_0": "Having practiced what did before",
    "ai-tha-ap487:4.2_0": "as mere asking.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:4.3_0": "‘The fairy came forth,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:4.4_0": "Because of the first demon muse.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:5.1_0": "Whose son is your son,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:5.2_0": "from the Great Brahmā realm.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:5.3_0": "Current all around,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:5.4_0": "as the sunrise drew near.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:6.1_0": "thousand-spoked wheels",
    "ai-tha-ap487:6.2_0": "dear sir, my feet have been seen.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:6.3_0": "Whose son is your son,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:6.4_0": "how am we to know who you are?",
    "ai-tha-ap487:6.5_0": "The conflagration of the Holy One,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:6.6_0": "I don’t transmigrate.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:7.1_0": "no god nor fairy,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:7.2_0": "I’m not able to curse them.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:7.3_0": "and I don’t have developed the supreme,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:7.4_0": "I am the supreme persons.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:8.1_0": "theirs think this is the past,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:8.2_0": "the bonds of sensuality,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:8.3_0": "all defilements with corruptions,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:8.4_0": "I realized supreme awakening.’",
    "ai-tha-ap487:9.1_0": "He then heard his words,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:9.2_0": "this is term of affection,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:9.3_0": "“Student, the Buddha,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:9.4_0": "you sit on it.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:10.1_0": "I’ll honor them,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:10.2_0": "promote suffering,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:10.3_0": "After conquering all creatures,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:10.4_0": "I gave the Teacher.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:11.1_0": "There the Buddha sat down where",
    "ai-tha-ap487:11.2_0": "like a lion in a mountain cave.”",
    "ai-tha-ap487:11.3_0": "quickly throw them down",
    "ai-tha-ap487:11.4_0": "he came to the mango tree.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:12.1_0": "fine rice with flowers",
    "ai-tha-ap487:12.2_0": "And the Moon and Candana.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:12.3_0": "they swiftly grasp it,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:12.4_0": "and reconciled the world.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:13.1_0": "Having given the fruit of the Buddha,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:13.2_0": "flowering on a flower,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:13.3_0": "Candimasa, the Moon",
    "ai-tha-ap487:13.4_0": "I pay homage to the Teacher.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:14.1_0": "confident and settled,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:14.2_0": "You clearly seen that rapture",
    "ai-tha-ap487:14.3_0": "I sitd down unjured,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:14.4_0": "dig up the world.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:15.1_0": "When I heard my past deeds,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:15.2_0": "I were to present,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:15.3_0": "“Before and fruitless,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:15.4_0": "smells, tastes, and touches.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:16.1_0": "Twenty-five years have passed",
    "ai-tha-ap487:16.2_0": "heavenly delight,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:16.3_0": "unless they’ve got rid of this,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:16.4_0": "and he shall wield power.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:17.1_0": "For six years old is going forth",
    "ai-tha-ap487:17.2_0": "you’ll fall into human state.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:17.3_0": "thinking, “She will be a wheel-turning monarch;",
    "ai-tha-ap487:17.4_0": "I am mighty of the four primary elements.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:18.1_0": "The ocean called ‘the city’,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:18.2_0": "overcome by ill will,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:18.3_0": "If the color of all remained,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:18.4_0": "organized,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:19.1_0": "because of this sort of happiness",
    "ai-tha-ap487:19.2_0": "they will transmigrate.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:19.3_0": "having been worshipped by the Buddha,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:19.4_0": "whether human or divine.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:20.1_0": "When future lives are born,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:20.2_0": "will follow the opportunity",
    "ai-tha-ap487:20.3_0": "I went forth,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:20.4_0": "and that will be a mistress.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:20.5_0": "Having memorized the teachings,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:20.6_0": "you’ll realize quenching.’",
    "ai-tha-ap487:21.1_0": "Having understood this, the Buddha,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:21.2_0": "dig up the world.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:21.3_0": "who contemplates my armies",
    "ai-tha-ap487:21.4_0": "and he left without residue.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:22.1_0": "since the legal procedure of ejection was",
    "ai-tha-ap487:22.2_0": "intentions and aims as well,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:22.3_0": "give up human life,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:22.4_0": "they’re just like the Thirty-Three.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:23.1_0": "Those who are diligent and discerning,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:23.2_0": "this mother is extinguished.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:23.3_0": "I have no wealth on wealth,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:23.4_0": "of the Victory.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:24.1_0": "from the mother’s womb,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:24.2_0": "food and drink that she consumes—",
    "ai-tha-ap487:24.3_0": "May even my consent",
    "ai-tha-ap487:24.4_0": "whether the self is tossed.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:25.1_0": "At five years old",
    "ai-tha-ap487:25.2_0": "then he went forth to homelessness.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:25.3_0": "I was swept away by the hair,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:25.4_0": "I attained perfection.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:26.1_0": "searching for the past;",
    "ai-tha-ap487:26.2_0": "I don’t see anyone.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:26.3_0": "I died at thirty years of age,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:26.4_0": "that I presented my deeds.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:27.1_0": "‘Homage to you, O thoroughbred!",
    "ai-tha-ap487:27.2_0": "don’t supreme among men.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:27.3_0": "Following his instructions,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:27.4_0": "I’ve attained the state of grace.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:28.1_0": "I died at thirty years of age,",
    "ai-tha-ap487:28.2_0": "to see the word of the Buddha.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:28.3_0": "I’m not aware of any bad places",
    "ai-tha-ap487:28.4_0": "The fruit of the Buddha.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:29.1_0": "My defilements have been burnt away by practicing absorption—",
    "ai-tha-ap487:29.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "ai-tha-ap487:29.3_0": "and live without defilements.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:30.1_0": "It was truly for me",
    "ai-tha-ap487:30.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "ai-tha-ap487:30.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "ai-tha-ap487:31.1_0": "Attaining the four kinds of textual analysis",
    "ai-tha-ap487:31.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "ai-tha-ap487:31.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "ai-tha-ap487:32.1_0": "That is how these verses were recited by the senior venerable Mandiya.",
    "ai-tha-ap487:33.1_0": "The fifth, Candana, Vajjiyamāhita,"
}